@@TJvCustomInspectorItem.DisplayIndex
Summary
  Sorted index in the dsiplay parent.
Description
  DisplayIndex indicates the index after sorting this item is at in its
  display parent. Read DisplayIndex to determine the position at which the item is displayed or set
  it to a new index.
