  Sender - Reference to the edit control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomInspectorItem.EditCtrl
Summary
  Reference to the current edit control.
Description
  EditCtrl holds a reference to the current edit control or <B>nil</B> if the
